and it forces us

00:02:18.820 --> 00:02:22.180
to work in a polychronic
way, and that's

00:02:22.180 --> 00:02:25.540
against what our nature is.

00:02:25.540 --> 00:02:28.600
So in particular I'm very
interested in the idea

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:30.490
