way that it's measured

00:03:15.670 --> 00:03:19.150
is you ask people, how
much do you multitask?

00:03:19.150 --> 00:03:23.800
Well, this is not very
fruitful because research

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:27.670
has shown that people
can be off by about 30%

00:03:27.670 --> 00:03:29.650
