kind of artificial task

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:45.130
and watch how fast or
how well they switch,

00:03:45.130 --> 00:03:46.990
but that's artificial
and it doesn't

00:03:46.990 --> 00:03:50.110
begin to model all
the kinds of things

00:03:50.110 --> 00:03:54.850
we experience in real-world
work, like career trajectories

00:03:54.850 --> 00:03:58.720
and conflicts and social
pressures and deadlines

00:03:58.720 --> 00:04:02.270
and how tired we feel and so on.

00:04:02.270 --> 00:04:05.530
