is that if we really

00:04:05.530 --> 00:04:08.770
want to study people
and understand them,

00:04:08.770 --> 00:04:11.110
we have to go where people are.

00:04:11.110 --> 00:04:14.230
So we have to create
living laboratories.

00:04:14.230 --> 00:04:17.300
And that's what I do.

00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:20.350
